{"article_id":"sxCz3PPxK1slmbAX","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump threatened Tuesday to have the military \" build the remaining sections \" of the U.S.-Mexico border wall ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"appearing to revive a call","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to use Pentagon money","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to finish the project","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"ahead of a meeting with congressional Democratic leaders","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"opposed to the president ' s funding request .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"\" People do not yet realize","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"how much of the Wall ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"including really effective renovation ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"has already been built .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"If the Democrats do not give us the votes","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"to secure our Country ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"the Military will build the remaining sections of the Wall .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"They know","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"how important it is ! \"","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Trump vowed ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"capping a series of tweets","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"meant to set the stage for the White House summit .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"For their part , House Democratic Leader Nancy Pelosi and Senate Democratic Leader Chuck Schumer put out a joint statement Monday","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"arguing","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Trump and his party will own a government shutdown","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"if they can ' t strike a deal .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"`` Republicans still control the House , the Senate and the White House ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"and they have the power","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"to keep government open , ''","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"they said .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"`` Our country can not afford a Trump Shutdown , ''","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"the Democrats said ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"that Trump `` knows full well","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that his wall proposal does not have the votes","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"to pass the House and Senate","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"and should not be an obstacle to a bipartisan agreement . ''","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Congress last week temporarily averted a partial shutdown amid the funeral services for the late President George H.W . Bush ,","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"pushing the new deadline to Dec. 21 .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Trump was meeting at the White House Tuesday with Pelosi and Schumer","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"to discuss a new government spending package","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"- with border wall funding the biggest sticking point .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"The Democratic leaders arrived at the White House shortly before noon .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Trump wants $ 5 billion for the project ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"while Democrats are offering $ 1.3 billion for border security .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"The president earlier this year pushed for military funding to finance the border project .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"while administrations can move some money around in their budgets ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"they need approval from Congress","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"- and the relevant appropriations bills for fiscal 2019 did not include money for this purpose .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Top Democrats also warned earlier this year","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"that the Pentagon would not have the power","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"to redirect funding to the border wall .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"But Trump ' s tweets marked the latest effort on both sides","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"to project a strong negotiating position .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"The president also claimed","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"that the wall and fencing","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"already in place","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"helped turn back the migrant caravans","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"forming in Mexico .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"He accused Democrats of sacrificing border security for political reasons ,","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"even suggesting","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Pelosi is holding up funding for a border wall","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"in order to secure votes for the speakership in the next Congress .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"\" We have already built large new sections & fully renovated others ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"making them like new .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"The Democrats ... however ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"for strictly political reasons","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"and because they have been pulled so far left ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"do NOT want Border Security .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"They want Open Borders","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"for anyone to come in .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"This brings large scale crime and disease , \"","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"\" Our Southern Border is now Secure","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and will remain that way ...","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"I look forward to my meeting with Chuck Schumer & Nancy Pelosi .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"In 2006 , Democrats voted for a Wall ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"and they were right to do so .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Today , they no longer want Border Security .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"They will fight it at all cost ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"and Nancy must get votes for Speaker .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"But the Wall will get built . \"","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Pelosi does face pressure from her base","depth":4},{"id":80,"text":"not to bend on the border wall funding fight .","depth":4},{"id":81,"text":"But more than the speaker ' s gavel is at stake -","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"Democratic votes in both the House and Senate could be critical","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"for averting a partial shutdown .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Sixty votes are required in the Senate","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"to overcome a filibuster .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"And , at least for the near-term , Republicans only have 51 members .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Republicans for the rest of the month have a comfortable majority in the House ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"but lack the votes on their side alone","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"to pass a bill with or without wall money .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Pelosi and Schumer have urged Trump to support a bill","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that includes a half-dozen government funding bills","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"largely agreed upon by lawmakers ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"along with a separate measure","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that funds the Department of Homeland Security at current levels through Sept. 30 .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Democrats will likely push for a continuing resolution","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"that funds the remaining appropriations bills","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"if Trump does n't agree to that ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"an aide told The Associated Press .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Trump said Friday","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"that Congress should provide all the money","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"he wants","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"for the wall","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"and called illegal immigration a `` threat to the well-being of every American community . ''","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"Pelosi said","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"she and many other Democrats consider the wall `` immoral , ineffective and expensive . ''","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"Schumer said","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"Democrats want to work with Trump","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"to avert a shutdown ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"but said","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"money for border security should not include the concrete wall","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Trump has envisioned .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"Instead , the money should be used for fencing and technology","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"experts say","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"is appropriate ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"`` We do not want to let a Trump temper tantrum govern our policies","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"or cause the shutdown of a government ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"which everyone on both sides of the aisle knows","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"is the wrong idea , ''","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"If Trump `` wants to shut down the government over Christmas over the wall ,","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"that 's his decision , ''","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"But House Majority Whip Steve Scalise , R-La. , said","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"Democrats were the ones playing politics .","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"Trump `` wants to secure the border .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"He got elected president on that platform , ''","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"Scalise told .","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"If there 's a better way","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"to secure the border","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"than the $ 5 billion plan","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"Trump has laid out ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"Democrats `` need to come with an alternative , ''","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Scalise said Monday .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":271,"left":214,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":170,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":153,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":141,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":0,"right":140,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":1